<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Welcome to Switchgate</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial, sans-serif; background: #f9fafb; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    .container { max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto; background: #ffffff; padding: 24px; }
    .brand { font-weight: 700; color: #01796F; }
    .card { background: #e6f2f0; border: 1px solid #01796F; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; }
    .cta { display: inline-block; background: #01796F; color: #ffffff; padding: 10px 16px; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none; margin-top: 12px; }
    .footer { font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280; margin-top: 24px; }
    a { color: #01796F; text-decoration: none; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="brand">Switchgate</div>

    <h2>Welcome, {{userName}}!</h2>

    <p>We’re excited to have you on Switchgate. Your account has been created successfully.</p>

    <div class="card">
      <p><strong>Next steps:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Verify your email to activate your account.</li>
        <li>Secure your account with MFA for added protection.</li>
        <li>Explore your dashboard to manage services and settings.</li>
      </ul>
      <a class="cta" href="{{verifyUrl}}" target="_blank">Verify your email</a>
    </div>

    <p>If you didn’t sign up for Switchgate, please contact our support team at
      <a href="mailto:support@switchgate.com">support@switchgate.com</a> or <a href="tel:09031682798">09031682798</a>.
    </p>

    <p>Kind Regards,<br />Switchgate Team</p>

    <div class="footer">
      You’re receiving this because an account was created with your email address.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>